episodes.title: Interview with "Natureboy" cult leader
episodes.description:
Eligio Bishop, aka "Natureboy", speaks with a CBC reporter about the Corner Brook woman, Kayla Reid, who has joined his group in Costa Rica. For more on the story: http://bit.ly/2n9b8NQ
